```

Buffer Pool Tuning

The buffer pool prevents GC pressure in high-throughput scenarios. Increase from the default 100 to 256 for production:

```javascript
// In RuVectorBackend config:
const bufferPoolSize = Math.min(
  Math.max(1, config.bufferPoolSize ?? 256), // Increased from 100
  1000
);
```

